 14 Step one - copy system lynx.cfg:
 13  
 12 cp /etc/lynx.cfg ~/.lynx.cfg 
 11  
 10 Step two - modify your ~/.lynx.cfg to your heart's content.
  9  
  8 Step three - launch lynx with your custom cfg:
  7  
  6 lynx -cfg=~/.lynx.cfg <url>
  5  
  4 Or easier add an alias to your .bashrc
  3  
  2 $ nvim .bashrc
  1 alias ?="lynx -cfg=~/.lynx.cfg"  
  
                                                           


